/*!
\page handle_drawnow DRAWNOW Flush the Event Queue

<p>
Section: \ref sec_handle "Handle-Based Graphics"
\section Usage
The <tt>drawnow</tt> function can be used to process the events in the
event queue of the FreeMat application.  The syntax for its use
is
\verbatim
   drawnow
\endverbatim
Now that FreeMat is threaded, you do not generally need to call this
function, but it is provided for compatibility.
*/
